    <item>
      <title>日本首相岸田致歉并承诺改革道德委员会</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-29/japan-s-pm-kishida-apologizes-vows-reform-in-ethics-panel</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本首相岸田文雄在周四现场直播的史无前例的议会道德听证会上，就行贿丑闻引起的公众不信任道歉，并承诺改革监管规定。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-29/japan-s-pm-kishida-apologizes-vows-reform-in-ethics-panel</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 29 Feb 2024 10:26:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>行长警告匈牙利央行独立性面临风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-29/hungarian-central-bank-s-independence-under-attack-governor</link>
      <description><![CDATA[匈牙利央行行长捷尔吉·马托尔奇 (Gyorgy Matolcsy) 表示，匈牙利总理欧尔班·维克多 (Viktor Orban) 政府正计划对央行独立性进行“重大攻击”，并提议修改监管该机构的法律。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-29/hungarian-central-bank-s-independence-under-attack-governor</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 29 Feb 2024 09:19:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>加沙数十人等待援助遭袭击，死亡人数突破 30,000 人</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-02-29/urgent-strike-on-palestinians-waiting-for-aid-in-gaza-kills-and-wounds-dozens</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加沙地带拉法（美联社）卫生官员称，周四早些时候，加沙城等待人道主义援助的巴勒斯坦人遭到袭击，造成至少 70 人死亡，使以色列与哈马斯战争爆发以来的死亡人数达到 3 万多人。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-02-29/urgent-strike-on-palestinians-waiting-for-aid-in-gaza-kills-and-wounds-dozens</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 29 Feb 2024 08:58:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>截止日期临近，韩国与医生举行首次会谈</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-29/south-korea-seeks-first-talks-with-doctors-as-deadline-looms</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国政府与因抗议增加医学院名额计划而罢工的医生举行了首次会谈，因为他们重返工作岗位的最后期限迫在眉睫——或面临惩罚。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-29/south-korea-seeks-first-talks-with-doctors-as-deadline-looms</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 29 Feb 2024 01:01:20 GMT</pubDate>
